import React from 'react';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';

import './NavBar.css'

export const Nav = () => {
    return ( <
        div className = "nav" >
        <
        div className = 'div_logo' >
        <
        h2 > Pokedex App < /h2> <
        /div> <
        div className = 'div_menu_nav' >
        <
        div className = 'div_link' >
        <
        Link to = '/home'
        className = "link" >
        Inicio <
        /Link> <
        /div> <
        div className = 'div_link' >
        <
        Link to = "#"
        className = "link" >
        Crea Tu Pokemon <
        /Link>	 <
        /div> <
        /div> <
        /div>
    );
};

export default Nav;
